sources.title: Clancy in Wall Street
sources.description: Title: Clancy in Wall Street Summary: Directed by: Ted Wilde Actors: Charles Murray, Aggie Herring, Lucien Littlefield Production Company: Edward Small Productions Release Date: 15 March 1930 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.20 : 1 Add Full Plot

metadata.Plot: A plumber accidentally purchases stocks in the stock market which quickly rise in value, leading the plumber to crash high society.
metadata.Writer: Ralph W. Bell, William Francis Dugan, Jack Wagner
metadata.Actors: Charles Murray, Aggie Herring, Lucien Littlefield
